<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於開始了呢～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天究竟會發射幾發煙火呢～<delay frames="40" />
呵呵，<delay20 />真是令人期待～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />期待已久的煙火大會終於開始了！<delay frames="40" />
我也好想像夜空中的煙火一樣
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />盡情地綻放啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚的煙火大會<delay8 />
才剛開始不久喔！<delay frames="40" />
一起來享受這次的大會吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火<delay8 />真是壯觀啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經搞不清楚<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底發射過幾發煙火了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當大量的煙火一口氣發射到空中時，<delay20 />
天空就顯得很熱鬧呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />月亮也有好好享受這場煙火大會嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />碰——！<delay20 />碰——！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好大的聲響啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發出這麼大的聲音，<delay20 /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
連肚子叫的聲音都被蓋掉了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火雖然漂亮，<delay8 />但同時也很神奇呢。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底是靠著什麼原理，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能像那樣發出各種顏色的光芒啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有看到<delay8 />剛剛的煙火嗎！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的超漂亮的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />你有好好享受嗎～？<delay frames="40" />
我打算觀賞煙火到最後，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你不嫌棄的話，我們一起看吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />離煙火大會結束的時間<delay8 />
也越來越近了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來的煙火我一發都不會看漏喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有欣賞到<delay8 />很多煙火嗎～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你有推薦的煙火，<delay20 />
記得要告訴我喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>